2| Prepare single-cell suspensions by mild enzymatic dissociation using a trypsin/EDTA solution9. Transfer stock cultures every 3–4 d by seeding appropriate numbers of cells of (0.5–1) Â 106 (depending on cell type and doubling time) into T75 culture ﬂasks. Avoid repeated dissociation of monolayers within less than 2 d.

